}}'''Denmark''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in March 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Copenhagen, along with Aarhus.

Denmark was part of a March 2019 [[Updates|update]] that added 8 new countries into the game. The other 7 were [[Portugal]], [[Norway]], [[Indonesia]], [[Singapore]], [[Finland]], [[Estonia]], and [[Romania]]. This update was also the update that brought [[Pets]] for the first time. This update was also the first to have multiple new countries being added other than the ones originally released.
